{"tid":1633583,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[是日行動post] 中庸之道 大家根本無共識今日休息定開花 原來大家搞錯左方向","createTime":"2019-10-07T04:31:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T04:48:23.000Z","uid":1212,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6ecd85c7867e8a870727cf813b2e365d76b84e1c","tid":1633583,"uid":1212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:31:58.000Z","msg":"現在大家不單連登都係未有共識 究竟係3點 定 8 點開花 定係休息日<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n開花手足就話 <br />\n休你老母 要繼續開花/攰撚死班狗<br />\n<br />\n休息手足就話<br />\n要抖下等美國過法例/比文宣做下野/敵擁我反(敵人派人製造混亂如燒站)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大家各執己見，搵唔到共識係到晒時間嘈，咁咪取中庸之道<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">今晚大家no gear 8點係18區商場唱歌喊口號<br />\n之後和平散 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n暫緩裝修暫緩暴力畫面</span></span><br />\n<br />\n同時文宣要keep 住做 去紅黑商店<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">裝飾</span><br />\n<br />\n如果大家認同的就<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">分享 傳開去 </span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"2f1e9ba70578a1ad07a8dd2895090271ab38157d","tid":1633583,"uid":1212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:32:14.000Z","msg":"推一推 好輕鬆"},{"pid":"6f2cd60d48c7cad31eca413ee53bcfd136ccd500","tid":1633583,"uid":1212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:33:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/10/07/123324_26df936371ec2db6f04b4e9edfc2c689.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F10%2F07%2F123324_26df936371ec2db6f04b4e9edfc2c689.png&h=2f54d682&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a9c47c47459defc2d9b13bdba4ea84d51479cc5c","tid":1633583,"uid":1212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:34:48.000Z","msg":"推一推"},{"pid":"cc62de8d15567e2abfbdac187e4ee8410b0764f4","tid":1633583,"uid":203152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:48:23.000Z","msg":"推"}]}